{
  "stem": "1062.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If he's going to be caught with the stuff, he's going to be shot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people were very frightened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A lot of people had some gold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, whatever they could get, money, something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took it along because we didn't know where we-- where we were going.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then one day, they took some women in one side, I'm talking-- I mean, Nazi woman, Nazi woman-- and Nazi men on the other side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they lined us all up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we went through and they searched us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some of them were strip-searched, women were searched, you know, every place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as they searched us, they told us to go right across the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a park.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We all went to the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And around that park, all the houses around that park, that was the main ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And from that park, we stayed there like, a night, overnight, in park.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The following day, they said, all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everybody go into the houses there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because what they did during that period, they took away the Gentile people who lived there and they moved them out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the Jews were moved into this-- to this-- to this spot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were-- and, and this area was closed in with a fence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they had the-- by the way, the Hungarian police who watched us, they were not the local police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were called border, border police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were the border police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were known as [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] are very rude, very cruel people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And from time to time, they would come into the ghetto just because of brutality.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they would beat-- my mother's brother was beaten up once.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They just beat him up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In the ghetto, there was nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they told everybody-- we were in one room, like maybe in a little room, we were mashed, I mean, maybe 20 people, 25 people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You know, hardly for people to lay down, one next to the other, and sleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they told us to dig outside the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to dig for latrines, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Trenches.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a rabbi there who said that if Jewish man and woman get married, if boys and girls get married, this is [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] means it's a redemption.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a mitzvah to get married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember everybody was grabbing, and they were running and getting married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the interesting part of this, the rich people would marry poor girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, because if you marry-- a rich man marries a poor girl, it's even more of a mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they tried to make mitzvahs over there, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because people, they believed in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, this was a way of life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in the ghetto, you know, there were children there too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember certain instances there where the children, they didn't have a-- the children, see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When you get up in the morning, we were taught to say the Modeh Ani.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to recite a certain prayer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every child was trained when you get up in the morning to recite the Modeh Ani before you could eat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the children would cry for food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was one woman there, her name was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sodarifca. ?] And she said, all right, children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Come together.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Before you eat, you have to recite the Modeh Ani.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she would have our Modeh Ani, which would last, like an hour and a half, two hours, thinking by the time she's going to be finished with this prayer, with the Modeh Ani, the children will forget that they-- that they are hungry, you know?",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And many times when I think back, you know, those are the things-- those are the things that eats at me, even today.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is something, you know, for the children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they were hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Certain things, when I think back today, big things, what people here may think is big, doesn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] But little things like this, which, you know, I don't know if it's little, but does eats at me even today.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] Anyway.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] We were in the ghetto, and then a rumor started to go around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one of the rumors was that we are going to be exchanged for German prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Another rumor was that they're going to take us to Madagascar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know why, but there was a rumor spread in the ghetto that we're going to go to Madagascar.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Another rumor was that we are going to be taken [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There's a river which is called the Danube.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Transylvania. ?] We will be taken to Transylvania to work the fields over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "All kinds of rumors.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
